<L>__{exterior open country moving shot ethan and mose dusk}
<A>__{(note to w. hoch: what we are trying to get here is that moment of swift transition from twilight to night; of riders briefly touched with the last colors of day and then, as they pass, becoming one with blue shadows of night.) ethan and mose are holding their mounts to a jog, in marked contrast to the all out pace of the others. the camera pans after them as the dark fingers of the night stretch across the valley. the wind begins to rise and somewhere off in the hills a coyote pack yaps.}
